we have created table and its values successfully ,now if we want to change table name or field name or add or delete we use alter command
to modify-only to change column definition,add or drop the table and its field name.
ALTER TABLE EMPLOYEE ADD EMPAGE VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL AFTER NAME;
DROP TABLE EMPLOYEE;
ALTER TABLE EMPLOYEE MODIFY NAME  VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL FIRST;
inorder to change the name of the field use like this
ALTER TABLE EMPLOYEE CHANGE NAME EMPNAME VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL;

we change the definition of the column field
ALTER TABLE EMPLOYEE MODIFY NAME VARCHAR(20) NULL;
   
   
   
   to change table name 
   ALTER TABLE TINKU RENAME TO TINKUPREETHI;
